Saint Francis spent many years living alone in the woods.

5
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:08,600
有一天晚上 他看到一位天使在天空中燃烧着
Then one night, he saw an angel burning in sky.

6
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:10,870
他醒来时…
And when he woke up...

7
00:03:11,070 --> 00:03:13,300
有了圣痕
he had stigmata.

8
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:20,010
但孤独会对心智做奇怪的事
But loneliness can do strange things to the mind.

9
00:03:21,750 --> 00:03:24,480
最终 他死于一种也会
Eventually he died of an eye condition

10
00:03:24,580 --> 00:03:27,650
导致精神病的眼疾
that also would have caused psychosis.

11
00:03:31,130 --> 00:03:32,250
当心

12
