他随时会回来
He'll be home any second now.

28
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:03,500
但不管你想卖什么 我们都没兴趣
But we're not interested in whatever you're trying to sell.

29
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:06,570
我没想卖什么给你们
I'm not trying to sell you anything.

30
00:06:09,580 --> 00:06:11,910
我能进去一会儿吗
May I come inside for a second?

31
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:16,440
就用下洗手间 一会会儿
Just to use the restroom. It'll only take a second.

32
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:31,990
你家很漂亮 你在这里住了很久吗
You have a lovely home. Have you lived here a long time?

33
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:36,130
走过客厅 右边就是卫生间
The bathroom is through the living room to the right.

34
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,800
谢谢
Thanks.

35
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:44,270
你的丈夫通常都迟归吗
Is your husband usually late?

36
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:48,110
你说你估计他随时会到
You said you expected him here any second.

37
00:06:51,260 --> 00:06:54,820
走过客厅 你右边就是卫生间
Bathroom is through the living room, to your right.

38
00:06:59,460 --> 00:07:01,520
你能带我去吗
Would you show me?

39
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:08,660
我觉得你该给我带路
I think you should show me the way.

40
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,210
夫人
Ma'am.

41
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:19,570
我在尽量有礼貌
I'm trying to be polite.

42
00:07:19,820 --> 00:07:24,310
在我开始变得不讲理之前 我们可以再试一次
Now, we can try this one more time before I start to become unreasonable.

43
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:27,590
我很抱歉 先生 但我真的要你离开了
I am sorry, sir, but I really need you to leave.

44
00:07:27,690 --> 00:07:30,570
我真不知道你要干嘛
I don't quite know what you're planning.

45
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,830
嘿 弗朗妮
Hey there, Franny.

46
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:44,080
我要你坐在那边的椅子上 保持安静
I'm gonna need you to sit over there on that chair and be real quiet.

47
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:46,400
你能做到吗
Can you do that for me?

48
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:56,420
现在 你不如做个好主人
Now, why don't you be a good host

49
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:59,410
带我去卫生间吧
and show me where that bathroom is?

50
00:08:17,570 --> 00:08:19,830
很好
Well, all right now.

51
00:08:21,110 --> 00:08:23,060
进步很大
Onwards and upwards.

52
