州消防局长乔治·查诺维克说 已将此事告知
State Fire Marshal George Chanovec says every fire department in the state

56
00:08:37,350 --> 00:08:41,910
州内的每个消防部门 这种娃娃身长十五英寸…
has been contacted about it. The doll stands 15 inches high...

57
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:47,690
体内充塞了稻草 脚下有名字印花 A·E·萨顿
The bodies are stuffed with straw, and the name A.E. Sutton stamped on the foot.

58
00:08:47,790 --> 00:08:52,350
消防局长说 这种娃娃售价不到一美元 通常来说…
Fire Marshal says the dolls, which sold for less than a dollar and for usually...

59
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:14,440
你母亲呢
Where's your mother?

60
00:09:15,350 --> 00:09:17,440
我不可能离开她的
I couldn't leave her.

61
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:31,820
你为什么在日历上标记这个日期
Why'd you mark the calendar towards this date?

62
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:36,090
听着 我希望这事发生 可并不想看到它发生
Look, I want this to happen. I don't want to see it happen.

63
00:10:36,730 --> 00:10:39,220
几分钟后就结束了
It'll be over in a few minutes.

64
00:10:41,770 --> 00:10:43,800
我有事要做
I've got things to do.

65
00:10:50,210 --> 00:10:52,740
在这里看不到绞刑
Can't see the hanging from here.

66
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:56,210
只能听到
Just hear it.

67
00:10:58,590 --> 00:11:00,480
听到？
Hear it?

68
00:11:00,990 --> 00:11:04,120
没错 绞刑听上去和看上去一样惨
Yeah, hanging sounds almost as bad as it looks.

69
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:08,790
活门砰地一开
Trap door bangs open.

70
00:11:09,700 --> 00:11:12,190
你想吃点什么吗
Do you want something to eat?

71
00:11:14,230 --> 00:11:16,200
几个看的家伙很可能会…
Probably a few fellows watching will give a...

72
00:11:16,300 --> 00:11:19,100
- 爸爸  - …欢呼叫嚷
- Daddy?  - ...whoop or a holler.

73
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:31,920
怎么了
Trouble?

74
00:11:32,020 --> 00:11:34,910
他们跟我说 我去得太晚了
I got there too late, they told me.

75
00:11:57,580 --> 00:11:59,970
你母亲的事 我需要帮忙
I need help with your mother.

76
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:46,620
- 有什么问题吗  - 弗朗妮？
- Something wrong?  - Franny?

77
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:49,070
没 只是…
No, it's...

78
00:12:49,170 --> 00:12:52,120
- 我从没见过人这么少的镇子  - 弗朗妮
- just that I've never seen a lonesomer town.  - Franny?

79
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:55,170
好吧 这只是因为…
Well, it's just that...

80
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:57,830
- 所有人都不敢看着卡特莱特父子死去  - 弗朗妮
- everyone's afraid to watch the Cartwrights die.  - Franny!

81
00:12:59,370 --> 00:13:03,600
并不是所有人 那边的日历表明 有人一直在算着日子
Not everyone. That calendar there says someone's been counting the days.

82
00:13:03,780 --> 00:13:05,700
弗朗妮
Franny!

83
00:13:06,850 --> 00:13:09,580
弗朗妮
Franny!

84
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:12,090
你还得管好这个问题
You will have to take care of this.

85
00:13:13,990 --> 00:13:16,520
弗朗妮
Franny!

86
00:13:19,390 --> 00:13:21,800
我和小乔发现杜斯·马丁死了
Me and little Joe found Deuce Martin dead.

87
00:13:21,900 --> 00:13:23,670
- 弗朗妮  - 死了？
- Franny!  - Dead?

88
00:13:23,770 --> 00:13:26,530
弗朗妮 弗朗 弗朗
Franny! Fran, Fran!

89
00:13:26,630 --> 00:13:29,660
弗朗妮 弗朗妮 弗朗妮 弗朗妮
Franny! Franny! Franny! Franny!

90
00:14:52,390 --> 00:14:54,650
你在干什么
What are you doing?

91
00:14:56,190 --> 00:14:58,420
你需要缝针
You needed stitches.

92
00:15:08,070 --> 00:15:10,430
你笑什么
Why are you laughing?

93
00:15:34,160 --> 00:15:36,190
为什么是我们
Why us?

94
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:42,960
你们让我进去的
You let me in.

95
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:49,070
你以前就这么干过
You've done this before.

96
00:15:58,990 --> 00:16:01,250
你为什么这么做
Why do you do it?

97
00:16:06,930 --> 00:16:09,390
这感觉很棒
It feels amazing.

98
00:16:12,730 --> 00:16:15,160
你会杀了我 对吗
You're gonna kill me, right?

99
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:22,380
我为什么要杀了你
Why would I kill you?

100
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:24,700
你是我唯一的朋友
You're my only friend.

101
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:34,350
我要管好你
I'm gonna take care of you.

102
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:38,080
你在干什么
What are you doing?

103
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:44,460
从俄亥俄来的一路上都吃的这种食物？
Been eating this kind of food all the way from Ohio?

104
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:45,580
是的 先生
We have, sir.

105
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:48,960
好吧 你再一直分给他 你就没得剩了
Well, you keep shoveling it out to him, you're not gonna have any left.

106
00:17:49,460 --> 00:17:50,770
你们要去哪
Where are you headed?

107
00:17:50,870 --> 00:17:53,430
我们想在这周结束前到斯莱特斯维尔
We hope to be in Slatersville by week's end.

108
00:17:53,530 --> 00:17:56,770
听说那里有个又大又富饶的山谷
Heard word of a large fertile valley there.

109
00:17:56,870 --> 00:18:00,730
如果可以 我们想买块地安定下来
And God willing, we hope to buy land and settle in peace.

110
00:18:01,170 --> 00:18:03,670
- 他不会再吵了  - …很贵啊
- He won't make any more noise.  - ...pretty expensive.

111
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:08,120
是啊 我们工作了很多年 把所有钱都存一起了
Yes, and we work for many years put all of our money together.

112
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:10,180
我爱你 爸爸
I love you, Daddy.

113
00:18:10,280 --> 00:18:14,010
开始一段全新的生活是我们的梦想
It is our dream to start a fresh new life.

